Okay, so here is ethnicity, which is counted separately than race.

98
00:10:00,818 --> 00:10:03,339
And just looked at ethnicity by ward.

99
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:07,860
We don't see a huge fluctuation, Hispanic, non-Hispanic by ward.

100
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:13,561
So with that, I'm gonna turn it over to Eunice, who is gonna talk about historic election results.

101
