233
00:27:39,221 --> 00:27:43,043
I'm only a resident here for five years and I've come from another community.

234
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:45,301
where there was ward representation.

235
00:27:46,182 --> 00:27:57,409
And I appreciated that because it gave me a person to contact if I needed to bring something up, you know, that was important to the city council.

236
00:27:58,310 --> 00:28:05,435
I've tried doing that in the past here in Medford to deaf ears, to be honest with you, which was really disappointing.

237
00:28:05,475 --> 00:28:12,059
So I basically had to go down to three, four counselors before I got an answer, even a reply.

238
00:28:14,397 --> 00:28:15,778
you know, to a question that I had.

239
00:28:16,879 --> 00:28:37,892
I think the hybrid approach is the right way, to be honest with you, because it does give you the ward counselor representation that you need for issues that you may have specific to your ward, but it also allows you to talk to the at-large counselors if you need something that's a little bit more overarching, you know, for the city itself.

240
00:28:42,735 --> 00:28:44,896
So no questions, more comments, I guess.

241
00:28:45,997 --> 00:28:48,239
No, thank you.

242
00:28:48,259 --> 00:28:49,139
Thank you for sharing that.

