248
00:29:28,856 --> 00:29:31,557
And if not, can you just give us an idea of what you're thinking?

249
00:29:36,832 --> 00:29:43,774
We have talked about term limits a little bit, but we haven't dived deeply into that yet.

250
00:29:45,834 --> 00:29:49,495
It is a question on our survey, which by the way, we have a survey.

251
00:29:49,955 --> 00:29:52,536
