00:30:01,018 --> 00:30:06,459
There is a section in the charter called transitional provisions that once we

254
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:13,263
make decisions on what recommendations we'll make and draft a charter.

255
00:30:13,604 --> 00:30:21,329
