00:32:58,803 --> 00:33:08,210
Yes, all the presentations from all our meetings are on the webpage on the city website medfordmed.org slash charter study.

286
00:33:09,231 --> 00:33:16,156
You'll find this presentation and any other presentation that we've had at our meetings.

287
00:33:16,237 --> 00:33:19,239
So you can see, you can look through the history of our meetings.

