00:33:25,564 --> 00:33:26,284
Thank you everybody.

293
00:33:26,304 --> 00:33:27,085
You're doing a great job.

294
00:33:27,855 --> 00:33:28,255
Thank you.

295
00:33:30,878 --> 00:33:31,339
Marilyn.

296
00:33:34,783 --> 00:33:37,246
Yes, Marilyn Davidson I'm in West Medford.

297
00:33:37,266 --> 00:33:41,170
I want to thank you all for so much hard work.

